{
  "video_id": "o4Nno6POrwE",
  "title": "It's time to reclaim religion | Sharon Brous",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Joanna Pietrulewicz"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12960.0,
      "end_time": 15176.0,
      "text": "I was a new mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15200.0,
      "end_time": 16456.0,
      "text": "and a young rabbi"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16480.0,
      "end_time": 18336.0,
      "text": "in the spring of 2004"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18360.0,
      "end_time": 20600.0,
      "text": "and the world was in shambles."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 21240.0,
      "end_time": 22496.0,
      "text": "Maybe you remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22520.0,
      "end_time": 25656.0,
      "text": "Every day, we heard devastating reports from the war in Iraq."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25680.0,
      "end_time": 29536.0,
      "text": "There were waves of terror rolling across the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29560.0,
      "end_time": 32240.0,
      "text": "It seemed like humanity was spinning out of control."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33000.0,
      "end_time": 34856.0,
      "text": "I remember the night that I read"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34880.0,
      "end_time": 37160.0,
      "text": "about the series of coordinated bombings"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37400.0,
      "end_time": 39736.0,
      "text": "in the subway system in Madrid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39760.0,
      "end_time": 41815.0,
      "text": "and I got up and I walked over to the crib"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41840.0,
      "end_time": 44256.0,
      "text": "where my six-month-old baby girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44280.0,
      "end_time": 46136.0,
      "text": "lay sleeping sweetly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46160.0,
      "end_time": 48495.0,
      "text": "and I heard the rhythm of her breath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48520.0,
      "end_time": 52960.0,
      "text": "and I felt this sense of urgency coursing through my body."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52120.0,
      "end_time": 56175.0,
      "text": "We were living through a time of tectonic shifts in ideologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56200.0,
      "end_time": 58856.0,
      "text": "in politics, in religion, in populations."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58880.0,
      "end_time": 60960.0,
      "text": "Everything felt so precarious."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61480.0,
      "end_time": 62736.0,
      "text": "And I remember thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62760.0,
      "end_time": 66360.0,
      "text": "\"My God, what kind of world did we bring this child into?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66960.0,
      "end_time": 70150.0,
      "text": "And what was I as a mother and a religious leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70400.0,
      "end_time": 71560.0,
      "text": "willing to do about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74840.0,
      "end_time": 77616.0,
      "text": "Of course, I knew it was clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77640.0,
      "end_time": 80536.0,
      "text": "that religion would be a principle battlefield"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80560.0,
      "end_time": 83160.0,
      "text": "in this rapidly changing landscape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83400.0,
      "end_time": 84736.0,
      "text": "and it was already clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84760.0,
      "end_time": 87480.0,
      "text": "that religion was a significant part of the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88120.0,
      "end_time": 89376.0,
      "text": "The question for me was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89400.0,
      "end_time": 91880.0,
      "text": "could religion also be part of the solution?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92480.0,
      "end_time": 94960.0,
      "text": "Now, throughout history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94120.0,
      "end_time": 97336.0,
      "text": "people have committed horrible crimes and atrocities"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97360.0,
      "end_time": 99000.0,
      "text": "in the name of religion."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 102616.0,
      "text": "And as we entered the 21st century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102640.0,
      "end_time": 107360.0,
      "text": "it was very clear that religious extremism was once again on the rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107760.0,
      "end_time": 109160.0,
      "text": "Our studies now show"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109400.0,
      "end_time": 112296.0,
      "text": "that over the course of the past 15, 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112320.0,
      "end_time": 114455.0,
      "text": "hostilities and religion-related violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114480.0,
      "end_time": 117416.0,
      "text": "have been on the increase all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117440.0,
      "end_time": 119696.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t even need the studies to prove it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119720.0,
      "end_time": 122896.0,
      "text": "because I ask you, how many of us are surprised today"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122920.0,
      "end_time": 126696.0,
      "text": "when we hear the stories of a bombing or a shooting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126720.0,
      "end_time": 129536.0,
      "text": "when we later find out that the last word that was uttered"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129560.0,
      "end_time": 132376.0,
      "text": "before the trigger is pulled or the bomb is detonated"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 134160.0,
      "text": "is the name of God?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 134400.0,
      "end_time": 136696.0,
      "text": "It barely raises an eyebrow today"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136720.0,
      "end_time": 138656.0,
      "text": "when we learn that yet another person"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 138680.0,
      "end_time": 141216.0,
      "text": "has decided to show his love of God"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 141240.0,
      "end_time": 143480.0,
      "text": "by taking the lives of God&#39;s children."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144680.0,
      "end_time": 147960.0,
      "text": "In America, religious extremism"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 147120.0,
      "end_time": 151656.0,
      "text": "looks like a white, antiabortion Christian extremist"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151680.0,
      "end_time": 154896.0,
      "text": "walking into Planned Parenthood in Colorado Springs"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 154920.0,
      "end_time": 156775.0,
      "text": "and murdering three people."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156800.0,
      "end_time": 159560.0,
      "text": "It also looks like a couple"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159800.0,
      "end_time": 160896.0,
      "text": "inspired by the Islamic State"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160920.0,
      "end_time": 165536.0,
      "text": "walking into an office party in San Bernardino and killing 14."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165560.0,
      "end_time": 170376.0,
      "text": "And even when religion-related extremism does not lead to violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170400.0,
      "end_time": 173416.0,
      "text": "it is still used as a political wedge issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173440.0,
      "end_time": 177536.0,
      "text": "cynically leading people to justify the subordination of women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 177560.0,
      "end_time": 180160.0,
      "text": "the stigmatization of LGBT people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 180400.0,
      "end_time": 183640.0,
      "text": "racism, Islamophobia and anti-Semitism."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184320.0,
      "end_time": 186416.0,
      "text": "This ought to concern deeply"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186440.0,
      "end_time": 189376.0,
      "text": "those of us who care about the future of religion"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189400.0,
      "end_time": 191616.0,
      "text": "and the future of faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191640.0,
      "end_time": 194160.0,
      "text": "We need to call this what it is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 194400.0,
      "end_time": 196200.0,
      "text": "a great failure of religion."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 197120.0,
      "end_time": 201960.0,
      "text": "But the thing is, this isn&#39;t even the only challenge that religion faces today."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 204400.0,
      "end_time": 205775.0,
      "text": "At the very same time"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 205800.0,
      "end_time": 209416.0,
      "text": "that we need religion to be a strong force against extremism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 209440.0,
      "end_time": 212456.0,
      "text": "it is suffering from a second pernicious trend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 212480.0,
      "end_time": 215280.0,
      "text": "what I call religious routine-ism."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 215840.0,
      "end_time": 218416.0,
      "text": "This is when our institutions and our leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218440.0,
      "end_time": 222216.0,
      "text": "are stuck in a paradigm that is rote and perfunctory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 222240.0,
      "end_time": 224296.0,
      "text": "devoid of life, devoid of vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224320.0,
      "end_time": 226400.0,
      "text": "and devoid of soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 226520.0,
      "end_time": 228896.0,
      "text": "Let me explain what I mean like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228920.0,
      "end_time": 231696.0,
      "text": "One of the great blessings of being a rabbi"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231720.0,
      "end_time": 236376.0,
      "text": "is standing under the chuppah, under the wedding canopy, with a couple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 236400.0,
      "end_time": 238656.0,
      "text": "and helping them proclaim publicly"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238680.0,
      "end_time": 241936.0,
      "text": "and make holy the love that they found for one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241960.0,
      "end_time": 243896.0,
      "text": "I want to ask you now, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243920.0,
      "end_time": 245815.0,
      "text": "to think maybe from your own experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 245840.0,
      "end_time": 247256.0,
      "text": "or maybe just imagine it"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 247280.0,
      "end_time": 250176.0,
      "text": "about the difference between the intensity of the experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 250200.0,
      "end_time": 251935.0,
      "text": "under the wedding canopy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 251960.0,
      "end_time": 255176.0,
      "text": "and maybe the experience of the sixth or seventh anniversary."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 255200.0,
      "end_time": 257656.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 257680.0,
      "end_time": 261576.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;re lucky enough to make it 16 or 17 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 261600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264576.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re like most people, you probably wake up in the morning"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 264600.0,
      "end_time": 268136.0,
      "text": "realizing that you forgot to make a reservation at your favorite restaurant"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 268160.0,
      "end_time": 269776.0,
      "text": "and you forgot so much as a card,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269800.0,
      "end_time": 272880.0,
      "text": "and then you just hope and pray that your partner also forgot."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 273959.0,
      "end_time": 276576.0,
      "text": "Well, religious ritual and rites"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 276600.0,
      "end_time": 280136.0,
      "text": "were essentially designed to serve the function of the anniversary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 280160.0,
      "end_time": 284176.0,
      "text": "to be a container in which we would hold on to the remnants"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 284200.0,
      "end_time": 287960.0,
      "text": "of that sacred, revelatory encounter"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 287120.0,
      "end_time": 289216.0,
      "text": "that birthed the religion in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 289240.0,
      "end_time": 291736.0,
      "text": "The problem is that after a few centuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 291760.0,
      "end_time": 294000.0,
      "text": "the date remains on the calendar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 294680.0,
      "end_time": 297536.0,
      "text": "but the love affair is long dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 297560.0,
      "end_time": 301856.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when we find ourselves in endless, mindless repetitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 301880.0,
      "end_time": 304960.0,
      "text": "of words that don&#39;t mean anything to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 304120.0,
      "end_time": 307856.0,
      "text": "rising and being seated because someone has asked us to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 307880.0,
      "end_time": 310776.0,
      "text": "holding onto jealously guarded doctrine"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 310800.0,
      "end_time": 314656.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s completely and wildly out of step with our contemporary reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 314680.0,
      "end_time": 317216.0,
      "text": "engaging in perfunctory practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 317240.0,
      "end_time": 320760.0,
      "text": "simply because that&#39;s the way things have always been done."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 322800.0,
      "end_time": 325575.0,
      "text": "Religion is waning in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 325600.0,
      "end_time": 329536.0,
      "text": "Across the board, churches and synagogues and mosques"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 329560.0,
      "end_time": 331160.0,
      "text": "are all complaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 331960.0,
      "end_time": 335976.0,
      "text": "about how hard it is to maintain relevance"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 336000.0,
      "end_time": 340136.0,
      "text": "for a generation of young people who seem completely uninterested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 340160.0,
      "end_time": 343816.0,
      "text": "not only in the institutions that stand at the heart of our traditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 343840.0,
      "end_time": 346416.0,
      "text": "but even in religion itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 346440.0,
      "end_time": 348480.0,
      "text": "And what they need to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 349280.0,
      "end_time": 352150.0,
      "text": "is that there is today a generation of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 352400.0,
      "end_time": 355896.0,
      "text": "who are as disgusted by the violence of religious extremism"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 355920.0,
      "end_time": 357616.0,
      "text": "as they are turned off"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 357640.0,
      "end_time": 360960.0,
      "text": "by the lifelessness of religious routine-ism."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 362440.0,
      "end_time": 366480.0,
      "text": "Of course there is a bright spot to this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 366960.0,
      "end_time": 371256.0,
      "text": "Given the crisis of these two concurrent trends in religious life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 371280.0,
      "end_time": 374976.0,
      "text": "about 12 or 13 years ago, I set out to try to determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 375000.0,
      "end_time": 376536.0,
      "text": "if there was any way"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 376560.0,
      "end_time": 380736.0,
      "text": "that I could reclaim the heart of my own Jewish tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 380760.0,
      "end_time": 383376.0,
      "text": "to help make it meaningful and purposeful again"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 383400.0,
      "end_time": 384840.0,
      "text": "in a world on fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 385520.0,
      "end_time": 386936.0,
      "text": "I started to wonder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 386960.0,
      "end_time": 391960.0,
      "text": "what if we could harness some of the great minds of our generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 391120.0,
      "end_time": 395960.0,
      "text": "and think in a bold and robust and imaginative way again"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 395120.0,
      "end_time": 398216.0,
      "text": "about what the next iteration of religious life would look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 398240.0,
      "end_time": 401296.0,
      "text": "Now, we had no money, no space, no game plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 401320.0,
      "end_time": 402776.0,
      "text": "but we did have email."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 402800.0,
      "end_time": 406496.0,
      "text": "So my friend Melissa and I sat down and we wrote an email"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 406520.0,
      "end_time": 409376.0,
      "text": "which we sent out to a few friends and colleagues."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 409400.0,
      "end_time": 411215.0,
      "text": "It basically said this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 411240.0,
      "end_time": 413160.0,
      "text": "\"Before you bail on religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 414440.0,
      "end_time": 416616.0,
      "text": "why don&#39;t we come together this Friday night"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 416640.0,
      "end_time": 420760.0,
      "text": "and see what we might make of our own Jewish inheritance?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 421280.0,
      "end_time": 423895.0,
      "text": "We hoped maybe 20 people would show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 423920.0,
      "end_time": 426480.0,
      "text": "It turned out 135 people came."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 427000.0,
      "end_time": 429536.0,
      "text": "They were cynics and seekers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 429560.0,
      "end_time": 431296.0,
      "text": "atheists and rabbis."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 431320.0,
      "end_time": 433856.0,
      "text": "Many people said that night that it was the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 433880.0,
      "end_time": 438176.0,
      "text": "that they had a meaningful religious experience in their entire lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 438200.0,
      "end_time": 440536.0,
      "text": "And so I set out to do the only rational thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 440560.0,
      "end_time": 442696.0,
      "text": "that someone would do in such a circumstance:"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 442720.0,
      "end_time": 447656.0,
      "text": "I quit my job and tried to build this audacious dream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 447680.0,
      "end_time": 450720.0,
      "text": "a reinvented, rethought religious life"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 451520.0,
      "end_time": 453736.0,
      "text": "which we called \"IKAR,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 453760.0,
      "end_time": 456936.0,
      "text": "which means \"the essence\" or \"the heart of the matter.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 456960.0,
      "end_time": 459560.0,
      "text": "Now, IKAR is not alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459800.0,
      "end_time": 461616.0,
      "text": "out there in the religious landscape today."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 461640.0,
      "end_time": 465455.0,
      "text": "There are Jewish and Christian and Muslim and Catholic religious leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 465480.0,
      "end_time": 467776.0,
      "text": "many of them women, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 467800.0,
      "end_time": 471816.0,
      "text": "who have set out to reclaim the heart of our traditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 471840.0,
      "end_time": 477390.0,
      "text": "who firmly believe that now is the time for religion to be part of the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 477600.0,
      "end_time": 480560.0,
      "text": "We are going back into our sacred traditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 480800.0,
      "end_time": 482816.0,
      "text": "and recognizing that all of our traditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 482840.0,
      "end_time": 487135.0,
      "text": "contain the raw material to justify violence and extremism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 487160.0,
      "end_time": 491976.0,
      "text": "and also contain the raw material to justify compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 492000.0,
      "end_time": 494416.0,
      "text": "coexistence and kindness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 494440.0,
      "end_time": 499256.0,
      "text": "that when others choose to read our texts as directives for hate and vengeance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 499280.0,
      "end_time": 501895.0,
      "text": "we can choose to read those same texts"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 501920.0,
      "end_time": 505520.0,
      "text": "as directives for love and for forgiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 506120.0,
      "end_time": 507616.0,
      "text": "I have found now"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 507640.0,
      "end_time": 512120.0,
      "text": "in communities as varied as Jewish indie start-ups on the coasts"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 512880.0,
      "end_time": 514775.0,
      "text": "to a woman&#39;s mosque,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 514799.0,
      "end_time": 518455.0,
      "text": "to black churches in New York and in North Carolina,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 518480.0,
      "end_time": 520776.0,
      "text": "to a holy bus loaded with nuns"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 520799.0,
      "end_time": 524159.0,
      "text": "that traverses this country with a message of justice and peace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 525390.0,
      "end_time": 527895.0,
      "text": "that there is a shared religious ethos"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 527919.0,
      "end_time": 533576.0,
      "text": "that is now emerging in the form of revitalized religion in this country."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 533600.0,
      "end_time": 537736.0,
      "text": "And while the theologies and the practices vary very much"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 537760.0,
      "end_time": 540456.0,
      "text": "between these independent communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 540480.0,
      "end_time": 543896.0,
      "text": "what we can see are some common, consistent threads between them."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 543920.0,
      "end_time": 546959.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to share with you four of those commitments now."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 547800.0,
      "end_time": 550160.0,
      "text": "The first is wakefulness."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 550400.0,
      "end_time": 551935.0,
      "text": "We live in a time today"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 551960.0,
      "end_time": 554456.0,
      "text": "in which we have unprecedented access"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 554480.0,
      "end_time": 557376.0,
      "text": "to information about every global tragedy"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 557400.0,
      "end_time": 559856.0,
      "text": "that happens on every corner of this Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 559880.0,
      "end_time": 562576.0,
      "text": "Within 12 hours, 20 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 562600.0,
      "end_time": 565176.0,
      "text": "saw that image of Aylan Kurdi&#39;s little body"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 565200.0,
      "end_time": 567576.0,
      "text": "washed up on the Turkish shore."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 567600.0,
      "end_time": 569960.0,
      "text": "We all saw this picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 570920.0,
      "end_time": 573256.0,
      "text": "We saw this picture of a five-year-old child"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 573280.0,
      "end_time": 576720.0,
      "text": "pulled out of the rubble of his building in Aleppo."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 577160.0,
      "end_time": 579536.0,
      "text": "And once we see these images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 579560.0,
      "end_time": 582199.0,
      "text": "we are called to a certain kind of action."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 582520.0,
      "end_time": 586936.0,
      "text": "My tradition tells a story of a traveler who is walking down a road"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 586960.0,
      "end_time": 590496.0,
      "text": "when he sees a beautiful house on fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 590520.0,
      "end_time": 594550.0,
      "text": "and he says, \"How can it be that something so beautiful would burn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 594800.0,
      "end_time": 596616.0,
      "text": "and nobody seems to even care?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 596640.0,
      "end_time": 599736.0,
      "text": "So too we learn that our world is on fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 599760.0,
      "end_time": 603496.0,
      "text": "and it is our job to keep our hearts and our eyes open,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 603520.0,
      "end_time": 606550.0,
      "text": "and to recognize that it&#39;s our responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 606800.0,
      "end_time": 608656.0,
      "text": "to help put out the flames."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 608680.0,
      "end_time": 610736.0,
      "text": "This is extremely difficult to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 610760.0,
      "end_time": 614536.0,
      "text": "Psychologists tell us that the more we learn about what&#39;s broken in our world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 614560.0,
      "end_time": 616896.0,
      "text": "the less likely we are to do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 616920.0,
      "end_time": 618496.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called psychic numbing."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 618520.0,
      "end_time": 621790.0,
      "text": "We just shut down at a certain point."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 621520.0,
      "end_time": 625576.0,
      "text": "Well, somewhere along the way, our religious leaders forgot"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 625600.0,
      "end_time": 628896.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s our job to make people uncomfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 628920.0,
      "end_time": 630976.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s our job to wake people up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 631000.0,
      "end_time": 633136.0,
      "text": "to pull them out of their apathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 633160.0,
      "end_time": 634616.0,
      "text": "and into the anguish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 634640.0,
      "end_time": 638960.0,
      "text": "and to insist that we do what we don&#39;t want to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 638120.0,
      "end_time": 641456.0,
      "text": "and see what we do not want to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 641480.0,
      "end_time": 643856.0,
      "text": "Because we know that social change only happens --"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 643880.0,
      "end_time": 644936.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 644960.0,
      "end_time": 648840.0,
      "text": "when we are awake enough to see that the house is on fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 649760.0,
      "end_time": 651696.0,
      "text": "The second principle is hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 651720.0,
      "end_time": 653340.0,
      "text": "and I want to say this about hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 653364.0,
      "end_time": 655496.0,
      "text": "Hope is not naive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 655520.0,
      "end_time": 657456.0,
      "text": "and hope is not an opiate."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 657480.0,
      "end_time": 661536.0,
      "text": "Hope may be the single greatest act of defiance"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 661560.0,
      "end_time": 663896.0,
      "text": "against a politics of pessimism"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 663920.0,
      "end_time": 666336.0,
      "text": "and against a culture of despair."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 666360.0,
      "end_time": 668256.0,
      "text": "Because what hope does for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 668280.0,
      "end_time": 671550.0,
      "text": "is it lifts us out of the container"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 671800.0,
      "end_time": 674776.0,
      "text": "that holds us and constrains us from the outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 674800.0,
      "end_time": 678536.0,
      "text": "and says, \"You can dream and think expansively again."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 678560.0,
      "end_time": 680959.0,
      "text": "That they cannot control in you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 681760.0,
      "end_time": 684776.0,
      "text": "I saw hope made manifest in an African-American church"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 684800.0,
      "end_time": 687335.0,
      "text": "in the South Side of Chicago this summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 687360.0,
      "end_time": 689160.0,
      "text": "where I brought my little girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 689400.0,
      "end_time": 690256.0,
      "text": "who is now 13"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 690280.0,
      "end_time": 691976.0,
      "text": "and a few inches taller than me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 692000.0,
      "end_time": 694800.0,
      "text": "to hear my friend Rev. Otis Moss preach."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 695560.0,
      "end_time": 701550.0,
      "text": "That summer, there had already been 3,000 people shot"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 701800.0,
      "end_time": 704400.0,
      "text": "between January and July in Chicago."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 705400.0,
      "end_time": 708136.0,
      "text": "We went into that church and heard Rev. Moss preach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 708160.0,
      "end_time": 710960.0,
      "text": "and after he did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 710120.0,
      "end_time": 714376.0,
      "text": "this choir of gorgeous women, 100 women strong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 714400.0,
      "end_time": 716360.0,
      "text": "stood up and began to sing."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 717200.0,
      "end_time": 720336.0,
      "text": "\"I need you. You need me."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 720360.0,
      "end_time": 723400.0,
      "text": "I love you. I need you to survive.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 723720.0,
      "end_time": 725416.0,
      "text": "And I realized in that moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 725440.0,
      "end_time": 729160.0,
      "text": "that this is what religion is supposed to be about."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 729400.0,
      "end_time": 733736.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s supposed to be about giving people back a sense of purpose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 733760.0,
      "end_time": 735256.0,
      "text": "a sense of hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 735280.0,
      "end_time": 740216.0,
      "text": "a sense that they and their dreams fundamentally matter in this world"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 740240.0,
      "end_time": 742800.0,
      "text": "that tells them that they don&#39;t matter at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 743760.0,
      "end_time": 746536.0,
      "text": "The third principle is the principle of mightiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 746560.0,
      "end_time": 749215.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a rabbinic tradition that we are to walk around"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 749240.0,
      "end_time": 751536.0,
      "text": "with two slips of paper in our pockets."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 751560.0,
      "end_time": 754976.0,
      "text": "One says, \"I am but dust and ashes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 755000.0,
      "end_time": 756696.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not all about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 756720.0,
      "end_time": 760240.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t control everything, and I cannot do this on my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 760960.0,
      "end_time": 765136.0,
      "text": "The other slip of paper says, \"For my sake the world was created.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 765160.0,
      "end_time": 768280.0,
      "text": "Which is to say it&#39;s true that I can&#39;t do everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 769400.0,
      "end_time": 771240.0,
      "text": "but I can surely do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 772160.0,
      "end_time": 773815.0,
      "text": "I can forgive."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 773840.0,
      "end_time": 775400.0,
      "text": "I can love."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 775560.0,
      "end_time": 777550.0,
      "text": "I can show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 777800.0,
      "end_time": 778696.0,
      "text": "I can protest."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 778720.0,
      "end_time": 781896.0,
      "text": "I can be a part of this conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 781920.0,
      "end_time": 784776.0,
      "text": "We even now have a religious ritual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 784800.0,
      "end_time": 786160.0,
      "text": "a posture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 786400.0,
      "end_time": 789736.0,
      "text": "that holds the paradox between powerlessness and power."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 789760.0,
      "end_time": 790976.0,
      "text": "In the Jewish community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 791000.0,
      "end_time": 794296.0,
      "text": "the only time of year that we prostrate fully to the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 794320.0,
      "end_time": 795976.0,
      "text": "is during the high holy days."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 796000.0,
      "end_time": 798240.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a sign of total submission."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 798840.0,
      "end_time": 801896.0,
      "text": "Now in our community, when we get up off the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 801920.0,
      "end_time": 805415.0,
      "text": "we stand with our hands raised to the heavens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 805440.0,
      "end_time": 811560.0,
      "text": "and we say, \"I am strong, I am mighty, and I am worthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 811800.0,
      "end_time": 814440.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t do everything, but I can do something.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 815720.0,
      "end_time": 820616.0,
      "text": "In a world that conspires to make us believe that we are invisible"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 820640.0,
      "end_time": 822175.0,
      "text": "and that we are impotent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 822200.0,
      "end_time": 824936.0,
      "text": "religious communities and religious ritual"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 824960.0,
      "end_time": 828576.0,
      "text": "can remind us that for whatever amount of time we have here on this Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 828600.0,
      "end_time": 831560.0,
      "text": "whatever gifts and blessings we were given,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 831800.0,
      "end_time": 832816.0,
      "text": "whatever resources we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 832840.0,
      "end_time": 835176.0,
      "text": "we can and we must use them"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 835200.0,
      "end_time": 837776.0,
      "text": "to try to make the world a little bit more just"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 837800.0,
      "end_time": 839180.0,
      "text": "and a little bit more loving."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 839920.0,
      "end_time": 842856.0,
      "text": "The fourth and final is interconnectedness."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 842880.0,
      "end_time": 846136.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, there was a man walking on the beach in Alaska,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 846160.0,
      "end_time": 848960.0,
      "text": "when he came across a soccer ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 848120.0,
      "end_time": 850616.0,
      "text": "that had some Japanese letters written on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 850640.0,
      "end_time": 853976.0,
      "text": "He took a picture of it and posted it up on social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 854000.0,
      "end_time": 856696.0,
      "text": "and a Japanese teenager contacted him."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 856720.0,
      "end_time": 860496.0,
      "text": "He had lost everything in the tsunami that devastated his country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 860520.0,
      "end_time": 863216.0,
      "text": "but he was able to retrieve that soccer ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 863240.0,
      "end_time": 866256.0,
      "text": "after it had floated all the way across the Pacific."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 866280.0,
      "end_time": 869550.0,
      "text": "How small our world has become."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 869800.0,
      "end_time": 873896.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so hard for us to remember how interconnected we all are"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 873920.0,
      "end_time": 875120.0,
      "text": "as human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 876720.0,
      "end_time": 878696.0,
      "text": "And yet, we know"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 878720.0,
      "end_time": 881416.0,
      "text": "that it is systems of oppression"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 881440.0,
      "end_time": 885536.0,
      "text": "that benefit the most from the lie of radical individualism."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 885560.0,
      "end_time": 887376.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you how this works."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 887400.0,
      "end_time": 889336.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not supposed to care"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 889360.0,
      "end_time": 891816.0,
      "text": "when black youth are harassed by police,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 891840.0,
      "end_time": 894136.0,
      "text": "because my white-looking Jewish kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 894160.0,
      "end_time": 898550.0,
      "text": "probably won&#39;t ever get pulled over for the crime of driving while black."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 898800.0,
      "end_time": 902960.0,
      "text": "Well, not so, because this is also my problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 902120.0,
      "end_time": 905296.0,
      "text": "And guess what? Transphobia and Islamophobia"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 905320.0,
      "end_time": 908856.0,
      "text": "and racism of all forms, those are also all of our problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 908880.0,
      "end_time": 912336.0,
      "text": "And so too is anti-Semitism all of our problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 912360.0,
      "end_time": 914560.0,
      "text": "Because Emma Lazarus was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 914800.0,
      "end_time": 916400.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 919560.0,
      "end_time": 922896.0,
      "text": "Emma Lazarus was right when she said until all of us are free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 922920.0,
      "end_time": 924856.0,
      "text": "we are none of us free."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 924880.0,
      "end_time": 926960.0,
      "text": "We are all in this together."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 927800.0,
      "end_time": 931295.0,
      "text": "And now somewhere at the intersection of these four trends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 931320.0,
      "end_time": 936560.0,
      "text": "of wakefulness and hope and mightiness and interconnectedness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 936800.0,
      "end_time": 940616.0,
      "text": "there is a burgeoning, multifaith justice movement in this country"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 940640.0,
      "end_time": 942896.0,
      "text": "that is staking a claim on a countertrend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 942920.0,
      "end_time": 948550.0,
      "text": "saying that religion can and must be a force for good in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 948800.0,
      "end_time": 952960.0,
      "text": "Our hearts hurt from the failed religion of extremism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 952120.0,
      "end_time": 956336.0,
      "text": "and we deserve more than the failed religion of routine-ism."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 956360.0,
      "end_time": 960136.0,
      "text": "It is time for religious leaders and religious communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 960160.0,
      "end_time": 963536.0,
      "text": "to take the lead in the spiritual and cultural shift"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 963560.0,
      "end_time": 967256.0,
      "text": "that this country and the world so desperately needs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 967280.0,
      "end_time": 969415.0,
      "text": "a shift toward love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 969440.0,
      "end_time": 973336.0,
      "text": "toward justice, toward equality and toward dignity for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 973360.0,
      "end_time": 976800.0,
      "text": "I believe that our children deserve no less than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 977360.0,
      "end_time": 978576.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 978600.0,
      "end_time": 986124.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}